    <title>🇩🇪 Joule Studio: Create Joule Skills and Agents Without Coding (Bonn, Germany)</title>
    <updated>2026-02-22T11:19:32.228000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Dan_Wroblewski</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/72</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P data-unlink="true"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color="#FF0000"&gt;IMPORTANT: &lt;/FONT&gt;We have reached our capacity for the event. You can still register and you will put on a waitlist, and we will notify you a few days before if space opens up, which it often does.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P data-unlink="true"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="rule.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/295882i3E2967613A5D1256/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="rule.png" alt="rule.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P data-unlink="true"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;This is the all-new &lt;A href="https://groups.community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/gh-p/code-jam" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;SAP CodeJam&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;for &lt;STRONG&gt;Joule Studio&lt;/STRONG&gt;, the new tool in SAP Build that lets you create extensions to Joule so users can use SAP's digital assistant in their custom workflows.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_1-1767517380897.png" style="width: 1008px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/357932iCB056C27E1D17A23/image-dimensions/1008x553?v=v2" width="1008" height="553" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_1-1767517380897.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_1-1767517380897.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1767517349886.png" style="width: 944px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/357931iA51444693A4F56B9/image-dimensions/944x491?v=v2" width="944" height="491" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1767517349886.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1767517349886.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The CodeJam is intended to introduce you to the Joule Studio tool, so you can create your own:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Skills,&lt;/STRONG&gt; which let you create predefined execution flows, triggered by a user's prompt inside the Joule chatbot&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Agents,&lt;/STRONG&gt; which lets you define complex scenarios that the agent can execute by iteratively reasoning and interacting with their environment to achieve a goal, using a selected LLM,&amp;nbsp;and triggered by a user's prompt inside the Joule chatbot&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;The session will include a short, simple introduction to the SAP AI tools and some basic concepts needed for working with Joule Studio&amp;nbsp;&lt;SPAN&gt;–&lt;/SPAN&gt; such as AI Core, document grounding, embeddings, and what after all is an LLM.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Currently, the event is based on these tutorials: &lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/mission.joule-studio-codejam.html" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Joule Studio CodeJam&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1919560387"&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/60779i762EF2904875ADCE/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" alt="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1723046882"&gt;&lt;U&gt;&lt;FONT color="#FF0000"&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Prerequisites&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Bring your own laptop with power adapter and have a supported Web browser of either Google Chrome or Microsoft Edge. Other browsers are not supported.&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;It can be helpful to bring a tablet or second laptop, if you have, to have the instructions on a separate screen.&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1526533377"&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/60780i0E8681E679B867ED/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" alt="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1330019872"&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Location and Date&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;This is an &lt;STRONG&gt;in-person event&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;only&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;(not virtual) and is planned for&amp;nbsp;&lt;FONT color="#FF0000"&gt;&lt;FONT color="#800080"&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Thursday,&amp;nbsp;April 16, 2026&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/FONT&gt;from&amp;nbsp;09:00 - 15:00 local time in &lt;STRONG&gt;Bonn, Germany (CEST)&lt;/STRONG&gt;. The language of the event and the content will be&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;English&lt;/STRONG&gt;.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Event Address: &lt;FONT color="#800080"&gt;DHL Post Tower, Charles-de-Gaulle-Str. 20, 53113 Bonn, Germany&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Building/Room: &lt;/STRONG&gt;Post Tower/02.230 Washington&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Address (Entrance):&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;Platz der Deutschen Post, 53113 Bonn, Germany&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Address (Parking):&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;Charles-de-Gaulle-Str. 20, 53113 Bonn, Germany&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Upon arrival, please contact the reception desk at the Post Tower for accreditation.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color="#000000"&gt;More information:&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;The event is kindly being hosted by&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;DHL&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;– THANK YOU!&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;The instructor is SAP Developer Advocate&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/72"&gt;@Dan_Wroblewski&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color="#FF0000"&gt;Please note that spaces are limited! &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color="#000000"&gt;We can only accommodate &lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color="#FF0000"&gt;20 attendees&lt;/FONT&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;If you want to attend, register by clicking the &lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;EM&gt;Yes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;button in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;EM&gt;Will you be attending?&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;section above to the right. About 2 weeks before the event, you will be asked to confirm your attendance and will receive further instructions.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/joule-studio-create-joule-skills-and-agents-without-coding-bonn-germany/ev-p/14333499"/>
    <published>2026-02-22T11:19:32.228000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
