    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;I have set up SAP Build Work Zone, advanced edition and it is working fine, and I even provisioned users and I am the admin.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;But when I open site settings for it, under the Identity Provisioning tab, I see an error and the retry button is disabled.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1773342066098.png" style="width: 930px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/382750i807322E8280698CA/image-dimensions/930x222?v=v2" width="930" height="222" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1773342066098.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1773342066098.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;WHat does this mean? How do I fix it?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/tooling-sap-build-forum/error-with-identity-provisioning-tab-in-work-zone-advanced-edition/td-p/14347615"/>
    <published>2026-03-12T20:02:06.435000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
