    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;I have a bunch of questions. Is it possible for us to have a short call?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I have only one set of IAS groups but I have many tenants with WZ. But more importantly, the users I want to remove are not in any of those Work Zone groups — I did provisioning and they now appear in WZ advanced. Perhaps I did the provisioning wrong&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
