    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-blog-posts-by-members/working-with-dms-in-sap-build-process-automation-a-complete-api-guide/bc-p/14383270#M178579</id>
    <title>Re: Working with DMS in SAP Build Process Automation — A Complete API Guide</title>
    <updated>2026-04-26T12:26:00.186000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Dan_Wroblewski</name>
